00:17:12,687 --> 00:17:16,664
Upang magkaroon ng ilang kumpanya si Aries.

232
00:17:16,890 --> 00:17:17,890
Oh, nakikita ko.

233
00:17:18,360 --> 00:17:22,572
Nay, bakit wala si Jay-jay?

234
00:17:26,493 --> 00:17:27,869
Magkaroon ng ilang kahihiyan.

235
00:17:30,080 --> 00:17:31,581
Itigil mo na. Huwag kang umiyak.

236
00:17:31,896 --> 00:17:35,185
Tumigil ka na sa pag-iyak.

237
00:17:35,210 --> 00:17:37,145
Sasama ka sa amin.

238
00:17:37,170 --> 00:17:39,213
Ako, at ang Kuya Angelo mo.

239
00:17:39,214 --> 00:17:42,425
Ako ang iyong Auntie Gemma,
kapatid ng nanay mo.

240
00:17:42,967 --> 00:17:44,427
Ano nga ulit pangalan mo?

241
00:17:45,845 --> 00:17:47,971
Aries.

242
00:17:47,972 --> 00:17:49,848
Aries, wag kang umiyak, okay?

243
00:17:49,849 --> 00:17:51,643
Mananatili ka rito sa amin.

244
00:17:54,312 --> 00:17:55,312
Aries.

245
00:17:55,980 --> 00:17:58,482
Bakit sobrang payat? Madali kong baliin ang iyong mga buto.

246
00:17:58,483 --> 00:18:00,527
- Shh.
- Hoy, panoorin mo.

247
00:18:00,985 --> 00:18:02,570
Huwag mo siyang kausapin ng ganyan.

248
00:18:02,821 --> 00:18:05,489
Aries, siya ang Kuya Angelo mo, okay?

249
00:18:05,490 --> 00:18:06,491
Tandaan mo yan.

250
00:18:06,991 --> 00:18:08,176
Sige na.

251
00:18:08,201 --> 00:18:11,620
Aries, behave ka habang nandito ka.

252
00:18:11,621 --> 00:18:12,747
Maging mabuti.

253
00:18:13,456 --> 00:18:18,420
Babalik ka para sa akin minsan
Gumaganda si Jay-jay diba?

254
00:18:22,257 --> 00:18:23,466
mauuna na ako.

255
00:18:30,473 --> 00:18:33,935
Nanay!

256
00:18:35,478 --> 00:18:37,604
<i>Iyon na marahil ang huling pagkakataon</i>

257
00:18:37,605 --> 00:18:40,399
<i>Tawagin ko siyang "nanay".</i>

258
00:18:40,400 --> 00:18:42,694
At si Lola, at...

259
00:18:47,198 --> 00:18:48,198
Pst!

260
00:18:49,200 --> 00:18:50,200
Hey.

261
00:18:51,578 --> 00:18:52,871
Gusto mo bang maglaro?

262
00:18:54,727 --> 00:18:56,541
Hinihintay mo pa ba ang nanay mo?

263
00:18:58,782 --> 00:19:00,422
Mukhang hindi na siya babalik.

264
00:19:01,337 --> 00:19:02,756
kawawa ka.

265
00:19:07,802 --> 00:19:09,179
Aries.

266
00:19:10,638 --> 00:19:12,432
May sasabihin ako sayo.

267
00:19:13,641 --> 00:19:15,226
Gusto mo ba...

268
00:19:16,060 --> 00:19:17,811
sa halip na manirahan sa akin?

269
00:19:17,812 --> 00:19:22,650
Ipapa-enroll kita sa iisang school
bilang si Angelo, para magkasama kayo.

270
00:19:23,151 --> 00:19:26,738
At kapag gumaling na ang kapatid mo,
tapos ibabalik kita sa kanila.

271
00:19:28,080 --> 00:19:32,877
ayoko.
Gusto kong makasama si Jay-jay.

272
00:19:33,244 --> 00:19:37,582
Hindi, babalik si Nanay para sa akin.

273
00:19:38,082 --> 00:19:40,667
Halika, Aries. Manatili ka lang sa amin.

274
00:19:40,668 --> 00:19:41,961
Sabihin mo na.

275
00:19:46,633 --> 00:19:48,468
Nanay!

276
00:19:49,844 --> 00:19:51,638
sabi ko naman sayo eh.

277
00:19:51,805 --> 00:19:53,765
Pupuntahan ako ng nanay ko.

278
00:19:54,599 --> 00:19:56,434
Uuwi na tayo ngayon?

279
00:19:57,560 --> 00:19:59,395
Aries, makinig ka sa akin, okay?

280
00:20:00,078 --> 00:20:02,789
Mananatili ka kay Tita Gemma sa ngayon.

281
00:20:03,759 --> 00:20:05,594
Ipapadala ka niya sa paaralan.

282
00:20:06,069 --> 00:20:11,741
Bibilhan ka niya ng maraming laruan,
damit, at pakainin ka ng masarap na pagkain.

283
00:20:12,200 --> 00:20:14,828
Sinabi mo na sa akin yan dati.

284
00:20:15,179 --> 00:20:17,681
Pananagutan ko kasi
para kay Jay-jay diba?

285
00:20:17,997 --> 00:20:21,417
Siya lang ang mahal mo.
Pinagbibigyan mo lang ako.

286
00:20:21,960 --> 00:20:23,711
Hindi mo ako mahal.

287
00:20:24,212 --> 00:20:25,964
Aries, hindi totoo yan.

288
00:20:26,965 --> 00:20:29,926
bata ka pa,
hindi mo pa maiintindihan.

289
00:20:30,301 --> 00:20:32,971
Pinagbibigyan mo lang ako!

290
00:20:33,847 --> 00:20:35,974
Siya lang ang mahal mo.

291
00:20:45,984 --> 00:20:48,945
Jay-jay...

292
00:20:52,490 --> 00:20:54,367
Huwag kang umiyak.

293
00:20:55,326 --> 00:20:57,161
Jay-jay!

294
00:20:58,580 --> 00:21:01,374
kapatid ko!

295
00:21:01,457 --> 00:21:04,377
Stop crying, Aries, andito na ako.

296
00:21:16,848 --> 00:21:21,059
<i>Ngunit dumating ang araw sa kalaunan
nang sa wakas ay nakatanggap ako ng balita tungkol sa iyo, Jay.</i>

297
00:21:21,060 --> 00:21:24,355
<i>Kapag gumaling ka na,
at gumaling ka.</i>

298
00:21:27,572 --> 00:21:30,116
<i>Napakasaya ko noon.</i>

299
00:21:30,528 --> 00:21:31,987
<i>Pumunta ako para bisitahin ka paminsan-minsan.</i>

300
00:21:31,988 --> 00:21:36,533
<i>Ngunit nawala ang aking pagnanais na makasama ka,</i>

301
00:21:36,534 --> 00:21:38,953
<i>dahil marami nang nagbago.</i>

302
00:21:40,405 --> 00:21:42,907
<i>Nag-asawang muli ang nanay mo.</i>

303
00:21:43,041 --> 00:21:45,335
<i>Lumaki din ako. Nag-mature ako.</i>

304
00:21:45,835 --> 00:21:47,545
<i>Sa huli ay nagkahiwalay kami.</i>

305
00:21:48,296 --> 00:21:53,383
<i>Nalaman ko mamaya na lumipat ka
sa isang bahay na mas malapit sa lola.</i>

306
00:21:53,384 --> 00:21:56,596
<i>Kaya, nakita kitang muli.</i>

307
00:21:57,446 --> 00:21:59,265
<i>At masaya ako sa kung ano ang nangyari.</i>

308
00:21:59,766 --> 00:22:02,477
<i>Masasabi mo nang maayos ang pangalan ko.</i>

309
00:22:03,686 --> 00:22:04,771
Aries!

310
00:22:05,396 --> 00:22:06,230
Sino siya?

311
00:22:06,231 --> 00:22:07,732
<i>Tinawag mo akong pinsan mo.</i>

312
00:22:08,066 --> 00:22:09,191
Pinsan ko siya.

313
00:22:09,192 --> 00:22:12,946
<i>Hindi ko maintindihan kung bakit
akala mo ganyan, pero...</i>

314
00:22:13,404 --> 00:22:16,741
<i>Alam kong tatlo lang kayo noong umalis ako.</i>

315
00:22:16,866 --> 00:22:23,413
<i>Pero hindi ko naisip
mabilis mo akong makalimutan.</i>

316
00:22:23,414 --> 00:22:24,808
Hindi ka na naman nagsusuot ng tsinelas?

317
00:22:24,832 --> 00:22:25,541
saan ito?

318
00:22:25,667 --> 00:22:28,002
Ano iyon?
Nagsasalita ka ba sa Ingles?

319
00:22:28,336 --> 00:22:29,671
Nasaan ang tsinelas mo?

320
00:22:29,963 --> 00:22:33,216
Ah, inihagis nila ito
bubong ng plaza.

321
00:22:33,841 --> 00:22:34,926
sila o ikaw?

322
00:22:36,302 --> 00:22:37,302
pareho.

323
00:22:37,595 --> 00:22:38,595
Alam mo kung ano?

324
00:22:38,846 --> 00:22:40,556
Dati, lagi kang may sakit.

325
00:22:41,224 --> 00:22:43,664
Ngayon, napakapilyo mo.
Palagi ka ring gumagala ngayon.

326
00:22:44,268 --> 00:22:46,979
Buti na lang nahanap kita dito.
Paano kung nawala ka?

327
00:22:46,980 --> 00:22:49,147
Hindi ako mawawala.

328
00:22:49,148 --> 00:22:51,317
Ang plaza ang paborito kong puntahan.

329
00:22:51,567 --> 00:22:54,779
Ang ganda dito,
maraming bata ang naglalaro.

330
00:23:06,040 --> 00:23:08,001
Eto, suotin mo ito.

331
00:23:08,876 --> 00:23:10,854
Isuot mo muna ito. ayoko
makita kang nakayapak, okay?

332
00:23:10,878 --> 00:23:12,005
Masyadong malaki.

333
00:23:13,339 --> 00:23:14,339
Huwag maging mapili.

334
00:23:14,340 --> 00:23:15,425
Halika, bilisan mo.

335
00:23:16,342 --> 00:23:19,219
Madudumihan ang iyong sapatos,
madumi kasi ang paa ko.

336
00:23:19,220 --> 00:23:22,598
Kung ayaw mong madumi ang mga iyon,
pagkatapos ay huwag maglakad ng nakayapak.

337
00:23:23,224 --> 00:23:24,517
Para hindi ka rin madumihan.

338
00:23:27,270 --> 00:23:28,396
Bilisan mo.

339
00:23:35,945 --> 00:23:37,071
doon.

340
00:23:39,323 --> 00:23:40,323
Sumakay ka na.

341
00:23:44,328 --> 00:23:45,328
kaya mo ba?

342
00:23:46,956 --> 00:23:47,665
Oo.

343
00:23:47,666 --> 00:23:48,915
Aalis na ako ngayon, okay?

344
00:23:48,916 --> 00:23:49,916
Pumunta ka.

345
00:23:51,794 --> 00:23:52,794
Tara na.

346
00:23:52,795 --> 00:23:53,795
Hey.

347
00:23:54,047 --> 00:23:55,840
- Ano?
- Ano ito?

348
00:23:56,174 --> 00:23:57,174
Masakit.

349
00:23:57,216 --> 00:23:59,343
Wala lang yun, wag mo na pansinin.

350
00:23:59,886 --> 00:24:00,970
Saan galing yun?

351
00:24:03,097 --> 00:24:05,349
Sinasaktan ka ba ng stepfather mo?

352
00:24:05,808 --> 00:24:06,808
Uuwi na ako.

353
00:24:06,809 --> 00:24:08,728
Sumakay tayo sa ating mga bisikleta bukas.

354
00:24:23,451 --> 00:24:26,370
<i>Sa araw na iyon, patuloy kong nakikita
na kotse sa lahat ng dako.</i>

355
00:24:26,871 --> 00:24:28,081
<i>Hanggang sa nakita ko sa school,</i>

356
00:24:28,372 --> 00:24:30,249
<i>at saan man ako pumunta.</i>

357
00:24:40,635 --> 00:24:42,553
Kailangan kong umuwi ngayon.

358
00:24:43,805 --> 00:24:46,807
Gabi na, baka mapagalitan ako
ng nanay ko. [Sa Japanese]

359
00:24:46,808 --> 00:24:47,809
[sa Japanese] Nanay?

360
00:24:48,184 --> 00:24:50,103
Nanay yan sa nihongo.

361
00:24:52,563 --> 00:24:55,358
Iyan ba ang sakay mo, Aries? Sino yun?

362
00:25:10,081 --> 00:25:11,791
Nandoon pa rin ang lalaking iyon.

363
00:25:12,291 --> 00:25:13,835
Laging sumusunod sa amin.

364
00:25:19,882 --> 00:25:21,050
Nanay?

365
00:25:21,259 --> 00:25:23,761
<i>Aries, nasaan ka?</i>

366
00:25:24,913 --> 00:25:27,164
<i>Kailangan mong umuwi kaagad.
Pupunta kami sa lola mo.</i>

367
00:25:27,306 --> 00:25:28,474
Bakit?

368
00:25:28,963 --> 00:25:30,923
<i>Nawawala ang kapatid mo, Aries.</i>

369
00:25:33,479 --> 00:25:34,772
anong nangyari?

370
00:25:41,612 --> 00:25:43,780
<i>Hindi ka namin mahanap noong gabing iyon.</i>

371
00:25:43,805 --> 00:25:45,849
<i>Pero hindi ako sumuko.</i>

372
00:25:52,790 --> 00:25:57,253
<i>Hindi ko alam kung bakit hindi agad
naisipan kong pumunta sa paborito mong plaza.</i>

373
00:25:59,255 --> 00:26:02,049
<i>Dahil lahat
biglang naging gulo.</i>

374
00:26:03,384 --> 00:26:07,929
<i>Nalaman ko ito kay mama at lola
na pisikal na inaabuso ka nila,</i>

375
00:26:07,930 --> 00:26:10,892
<i>lahat ng lalaking nakasama ng nanay mo.</i>

376
00:26:15,923 --> 00:26:18,760
<i>Sabi nila tumakas ka lang,
dugo sa iyong damit,</i>

377
00:26:19,609 --> 00:26:21,694
<i>at walang tsinelas.</i>

378
00:26:54,268 --> 00:26:55,519
Jay!

379
00:26:55,853 --> 00:26:57,104
Aries.

380
00:26:57,980 --> 00:26:58,981
Jay!

381
00:27:00,691 --> 00:27:01,691
Jay-jay!

382
00:27:09,617 --> 00:27:10,660
Jay.

383
00:27:11,911 --> 00:27:16,874
<i>Kung sinabi ko lang sa kanila kaagad
ang nakita ko sa leeg mo,</i>

384
00:27:17,708 --> 00:27:19,068
<i>Magiging ganito ka ba?</i>

385
00:27:20,127 --> 00:27:21,712
<i>Nasa police station si Nanay,</i>

386
00:27:22,046 --> 00:27:24,005
<i>sabi nila yung lalaki
kung sino ang gumawa nito sa iyo ay patay na.</i>

387
00:27:24,006 --> 00:27:26,050
<i>Ang dahilan ng lahat ng kaguluhang ito.</i>

388
00:27:26,259 --> 00:27:28,927
Ito ay malinaw na tanda ng traumatic disorder.

389
00:27:28,928 --> 00:27:33,432
Maaaring minsan ang dissociative amnesia
mararanasan ng biktima.

390
00:27:35,184 --> 00:27:37,770
Hanggang kailan siya mananatiling ganito?

391
00:27:39,563 --> 00:27:45,360
Depende ito, ngunit iminumungkahi ko iyon
dadalhin ang bata sa isang psychologist

392
00:27:45,361 --> 00:27:47,321
para sa paggamot ng kanyang trauma.

393
00:27:47,655 --> 00:27:50,408
Ang ilang mga sugat ay hindi pisikal.

394
00:27:50,533 --> 00:27:51,659
Ang mahalaga ay iyon

395
00:27:51,951 --> 00:27:55,413
hindi namin siya pinipilit na maalala
ang hindi pa niya handang harapin.

396
00:27:55,788 --> 00:27:57,373
Baka makasama ito sa kanya.

397
00:27:57,832 --> 00:27:58,832
salamat po.

398
00:27:58,833 --> 00:28:00,250
- Salamat, Doc.
- Mauuna na ako.

399
00:28:00,251 --> 00:28:01,752
Ilalabas kita.

400
00:28:06,382 --> 00:28:07,466
Jay,

401
00:28:09,260 --> 00:28:12,054
magpahinga ka muna.

402
00:28:12,638 --> 00:28:13,764
Oo.

403
00:28:32,992 --> 00:28:34,410
anong ginagawa mo

404
00:28:35,369 --> 00:28:38,539
Ano ang ginawa nila sa likod ko?

405
00:28:41,208 --> 00:28:42,501
May mga sugat ka.

406
00:28:44,086 --> 00:28:45,963
Saan ako nasaktan?

407
00:28:46,589 --> 00:28:47,923
Bakit hindi ko alam?

408
00:28:50,718 --> 00:28:52,344
Maaalala mo rin sa huli.

409
00:28:54,722 --> 00:28:57,516
Magpahinga ka lang, para mas mabilis kang maka-recover.

410
00:29:03,833 --> 00:29:05,710
nasaan si mama?

411
00:29:07,151 --> 00:29:08,486
hindi ko alam.

412
00:29:08,903 --> 00:29:10,488
Pero baka papunta na siya.

413
00:29:11,614 --> 00:29:14,075
Sasabihin ko sayo kapag nandito na siya, okay?

414
00:29:14,776 --> 00:29:16,903
salamat po.

415
00:29:25,127 --> 00:29:27,797
<i>Pagkatapos noon, nagsimula ka
nakatira kasama ang lola.</i>

416
00:29:28,506 --> 00:29:30,548
<i>Pareho na kami ngayon
hiwalay sa aming ina.</i>

417
00:29:30,549 --> 00:29:32,843
<i>Kaya, nagtaka ako...</i>

418
00:29:34,136 --> 00:29:35,804
<i>kanino ba talaga ang may kasalanan nito?</i>

419
00:29:35,805 --> 00:29:38,056
<i>Akin o kay nanay?</i>

420
00:29:38,057 --> 00:29:41,811
<i>O lahat tayo ay may kanya-kanyang problema,
na kung bakit hindi kami naging okay?</i>

421
00:29:44,021 --> 00:29:45,647
<i>Paano kung may nangyaring masama?</i>

422
00:29:45,648 --> 00:29:46,982
<i>May mas malaking problema ka!</i>

423
00:29:47,233 --> 00:29:49,068
<i>Maraming taon ang lumipas..</i>

424
00:29:49,707 --> 00:29:51,751
<i>At maraming nangyari
sa akin, at sa iyo.</i>

425
00:29:53,114 --> 00:29:55,533
<i>Maraming bagay
Hindi ko pa rin maintindihan.</i>

426
00:29:59,870 --> 00:30:01,414
Nakikinig ka ba?

427
00:30:02,206 --> 00:30:05,543
Damn it, babae ka at
nakikipag suntukan ka?

428
00:30:06,502 --> 00:30:07,420
Iniisip mo rin ba?

429
00:30:07,421 --> 00:30:09,130
Tama na, tigilan mo na.

430
00:30:10,631 --> 00:30:11,631
Jay?

431
00:30:14,844 --> 00:30:16,970
hindi pa ako tapos! Bumalik ka dito!

432
00:30:16,971 --> 00:30:18,431
Angelo.

433
00:30:19,265 --> 00:30:22,476
- Uy, Aries.
- Susundan ko siya.

434
00:30:23,352 --> 00:30:24,770
Kausapin mo siya.

435
00:30:42,288 --> 00:30:43,289
Ikaw ba si Jay-jay?

436
00:30:43,831 --> 00:30:44,697
Oo.

437
00:30:44,722 --> 00:30:45,842
Dito ka nakatira, tama?

438
00:30:46,917 --> 00:30:48,377
Kilala mo siguro ang anak ko?

439
00:30:48,794 --> 00:30:50,504
- Maaari mo ba akong tulungan, mangyaring?
- Anak mo?

440
00:30:50,796 --> 00:30:51,796
Oo, Aries.

441
00:30:51,797 --> 00:30:53,466
Jay-jay?

442
00:30:53,799 --> 00:30:56,010
- Ikaw ang ama ni Aries?
- Jay-jay!

443
00:30:59,805 --> 00:31:00,805
Bitawan mo siya!

444
00:31:02,725 --> 00:31:04,477
Pumasok ka sa loob!

445
00:31:05,462 --> 00:31:06,588
Hawakan mo siya, bilisan mo!

446
00:31:08,105 --> 00:31:09,105
Pumasok ka sa loob!

447
00:31:37,968 --> 00:31:38,968
Jay?

448
00:31:39,345 --> 00:31:40,513
Jay, nasaan ka na?

449
00:31:40,804 --> 00:31:41,847
Aries?

450
00:31:43,349 --> 00:31:44,807
Aries, nasaan ka na?

451
00:31:44,808 --> 00:31:47,353
Saan kami dinala ng mga lalaking iyon?

452
00:31:47,811 --> 00:31:48,787
Jay.

453
00:31:48,812 --> 00:31:50,689
Jay-jay, sinaktan ka ba nila?

454
00:31:51,273 --> 00:31:52,525
Hindi.

455
00:32:00,282 --> 00:32:01,282
Narito ang ilang pagkain.

456
00:32:01,367 --> 00:32:03,786
Sigurado akong pareho kayong gutom na gutom.

457
00:32:05,996 --> 00:32:07,206
sino ka ba

458
00:32:12,625 --> 00:32:13,876
Aries?

459
00:32:14,755 --> 00:32:16,382
Medyo magkahawig ang mga pangalan namin.

460
00:32:18,509 --> 00:32:20,718
Seryoso talaga ang nanay mo,

461
00:32:20,719 --> 00:32:22,513
kahit kailan hindi kita pinakilala.

462
00:32:24,807 --> 00:32:28,227
Sa pangalan ko lang,
